Project Name : - Blood Tracking Application


This project acts as an important role in saving the lives of human beings and also save time and money from black marketers. The project Blood tracking application develop so that users can view the info about which group of blood available in a blood bank or nearby hospital and the donor. The main aim of developing this app is to reduce the time to a great extent that is spent in searching for the right donor and the availability of blood required. Thus this app provides the required info in no time and also helps in quicker decision making.

1. Acknowledge FTDs reduce/prevent adverse events and the blood donor's anxiety.
2. Get live information about the different blood groups in a blood bank.
3. Use personal aspects to motivate blood donors.
4. Make blood donations convenient.
5. Distribute information aimed at dispelling misconceptions.
6. A donor could register him/herself from the app for any upcoming/ongoing blood donation campaign.
